 and red dynamically excited TNOs provide\nstrong evidence that their colors are due to different formation locations in a\ndisk of planetesimals with a compositional gradient.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Dec 2018 19:09:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-08"}
