 CIDEr-D on the Karpathy split, and a competitive\n$125.5$ CIDEr-D (c40) on the official server even compared to other ensemble\nmodels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Dec 2018 07:13:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 Dec 2018 05:09:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 11 Dec 2018 01:32:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-12"}
